item.title: Packing for Osaka
item.description: 22:52 Thursday 14 September 2017 JST Will be heading to Osaka tomorrow at 5am. Gonna hang out with Simon for two days. Boating, skating, and maybe recording a podcast. My skates are way too big to fit in my backpack, so I am taking a suitcase to hold them and my helmet. I never ended up getting wrist guards so I will skate gently and not fall down. I will take my computer and get some iOS programming done on the train.
